#.Os
#.Sh NAME
#.Nm libMainThreadHygienator
#.Nd tool to call out IO & XPC on an application's' main thread
#.Sh DESCRIPTION
#.Nm
Synchronous calls to disk or other processes through XPC on an application's main thread one of the leading causes of performance issues when a system is under contention.  This always-on-tool calls out this behavior.'
